divs: Sighting DetailsWalking out to my car to get something I look up in the sky and I saw a round cloud moving from a none clouded area towards the clouds but was moving faster than regular clouds and was going total different direction then as it reach clouded area you could still see it pushing through the normal clouds lost track in the clouds around 11:15 . Something unreal still in disbelief.
